{"tid":1874944,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"食光榮食到想喊","createTime":"2020-02-11T13:07:00.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-11T14:13:34.000Z","uid":173595,"like":13,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"6f74230e605373f0e4c03efaea0379ee75fdd764","tid":1874944,"uid":173595,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-11T13:07:00.000Z","msg":"自己一個坐係光榮食住個椒鹽豬扒飯。<br />\n自己完全控制唔到愈食愈急，就覺得好似每一次全日都無食過飯，經歷完生死，見到野食就狼吞虎嚥。今次我能夠自己一個坐係到，可能只係僥倖。<br />\n食嘅時候會不自覺諗到其他手足無啖好食，可能係好簡單一碟飯佢地都唔會有住何怨言，默默食完佢嘅飯，然後就諗下一餐飯要等到唔知幾時先食得。<br />\n每一次幫襯黃店，我個腦只會諗住手足。我就會好不自覺觀察在座嘅人，睇下有無係手足唔方便出聲但佢無錢食飯。唔知大家幫襯黃店嘅時候係諗緊啲咩呢？打住懲罰黃店嘅旗號去減少自己無做過野嘅罪惡感？定係真心為手足，唔想辜負佢地流過嘅血而去為呢場革命掙扎努力？<br />\n只能說我可能投入太多，每買一樣野我都會想盡辦法搵佢究竟係藍定黃，係因為幫襯一間藍店，每一棍每一槍我都好似有份咁，感覺滿手鮮血，手上件貨，口裏邊嘅野食都係鮮血。大家呢個時候，係咪真係做到全罷黨鐵，全罷食紅底飯呢？<br />\n打呢篇野唔係想講啲咩，只係想分洩下，怕自己抑鬱成疾。但當你曾經係條街到，你就根本抽身唔到，永遠都係呢個無底洞，好憤怒，好悲傷，叫自己唔好睇但每晚都留意到兩三點先瞓。<br />\n最後銀包僅餘嘅$50都放咗入火榮個捐款箱到，錢銀唔係咩咁重要，幫到幾多得幾多。心繫手足，我等你地每一個都平平安安出翻黎。走咗嘅手足，對唔住，到呢一刻都唔能夠重光......Sorry for 1999同打錯字，好少出post，勿插......"},{"pid":"12c144eadaf7a1f685cb7a2cfe237d901a39d4ce","tid":1874944,"uid":205482,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-11T13:09:05.000Z","msg":"借推行動post<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n一個銀髮族，勝過千個連登仔<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1874855\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1874855</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"83fed684d64ed50c727718d72586a202c1bba98a","tid":1874944,"uid":19126,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-11T13:09:53.000Z","msg":"巴打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"30245febc2669228f1317abfb785a49670d73138","tid":1874944,"uid":140538,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-11T13:16:08.000Z","msg":"咁食得安唔安樂？安樂就得啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"71e16c094192b18a891189ecf083c4fd9b5bb678","tid":1874944,"uid":212274,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-11T13:16:11.000Z","msg":"其實仲有好多人係可以分既野一定分黃藍幫襯,唔洗灰心"},{"pid":"305dec974b3a47034a539d417c2bb9ab9b66426c","tid":1874944,"uid":173595,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"83fed684d64ed50c727718d72586a202c1bba98a","tid":1874944,"uid":19126,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-11T13:09:53.000Z","msg":"巴打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-11T13:26:31.000Z","msg":"仲撐到，放心"},{"pid":"ed82376d38c99bb301dba23ffd01d161788b21b9","tid":1874944,"uid":19126,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"305dec974b3a47034a539d417c2bb9ab9b66426c","tid":1874944,"uid":173595,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"83fed684d64ed50c727718d72586a202c1bba98a","tid":1874944,"uid":19126,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-11T13:09:53.000Z","msg":"巴打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-11T13:26:31.000Z","msg":"仲撐到，放心"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-11T13:27:07.000Z","msg":"頂實啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e65af818dacb5f8e8d9734036977d1a753a1adf8","tid":1874944,"uid":38164,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-11T14:13:34.000Z","msg":"大家都神經緊張左好耐。但唔敢放棄"}]}